00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:41.000
And the advice was to do as much as you can with your eyes so that you will train it to, you will exercise it.

00:28:41.000 --> 00:28:47.000
Keep exercising it and get it so that it becomes to strengthen it so it's stronger.

00:28:47.000 --> 00:28:49.000
I don't know whether they were right or wrong.

00:28:49.000 --> 00:28:52.000
But I was doing it.

00:28:52.000 --> 00:29:01.000
And I did all the things that they asked me to do to strengthen the muscles in the eye and the eye and all like that.

00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:06.000
Until I could see what was happening on the television.

00:29:06.000 --> 00:29:14.000
And that was, you know, after a few months, that was really, really good news.

00:29:14.000 --> 00:29:19.000
But my brain was something else.

00:29:19.000 --> 00:29:29.000
However, my children didn't say to me, well, see what happened to you now.

00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:30.000
They didn't.

00:29:30.000 --> 00:29:32.000
They were there for me.

00:29:32.000 --> 00:29:34.000
And my family were there for me.

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:37.000
And I'm so grateful to them.

00:29:37.000 --> 00:29:50.000
So that was the beginning of my, of the real change in my growing, in my life.

00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:58.000
Because I have to learn to start living off pension and not able to work.

00:29:58.000 --> 00:30:01.000
In fact, I can tell you this.

00:30:01.000 --> 00:30:07.000
1996, I have learned, since 1996, I have learned a pay packet.

00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:10.000
I have learned my hand out for a pay packet.

00:30:10.000 --> 00:30:29.000
1996 till 2000, till 2000, I was, I was, 1998, 1998 till 2000, I was literally blind.

00:30:29.000 --> 00:30:43.000
